abbr: GNU Image Manipulation Programm


{ Selection

  { Magic Wand

    Change size of selection by holding mouse clicked and moving the mose up/down or left/right, respectively.
   (This was useful to select signature).

  }

}
{ Draw straight lines

  Choose »instrument« (pencil etc.), click, press and hold shift, click next point.



}
